TextEng: Pleased to meet you, Gilbert.
Hello, Gilbert. Me name be <FullName>.
I think I'll be going now.
Sorry, you must have me confused with someone else.
Text: 미안하지만, 나를 다른 사람으로 착각한 것 같아.

TextEng: Hi, Gilbert. My name is <FullName>.
Me name be <FullName>.
I think I'll be going now.
Me go now.
Me go now.
Me think you not know me. You thinking of some other one.
Text: 나 너 나 몰라. 너 다른 사람 생각하는 거야.

TextEng: Why do you want to meet Lady Aribeth so badly?
Text: 왜 아리베스 경을 그렇게 만나고 싶어?

TextEng: How's your training going, Gilbert?
Can I ask you some questions?
Why you want meet Aribeth so bad?
Text: 너 왜 아리베스 그렇게 만나고 싶어?

TextEng: How you training going, Gilbert?
Me want ask you some questions.
What can you tell me about the plague?
Text: 역병에 대해 뭘 알려줄 수 있어?

TextEng: Have you heard those rumors about a cure for the plague?
How do you like training here at the Academy?
What you know 'bout plague?
You hear stuff 'bout cure for plague?
You like training at Academy?
Sounds tough. How are you holding up?
Sound hard. You holding up good still?
Sounds like you've got a crush on her.
It sound like you maybe love her.
Don't worry - I still want to get together.
Text: 걱정 마 - 나 아직도 나중에 만나고 싶어.

TextEng: You no worry - me still want see you later.
Text: 너 걱정 마 - 나 아직도 나중에 보고 싶어.

TextEng: Actually, I can't get together with you later after all.
Text: 사실, 나중에 같이 있을 수 없을 것 같아.

TextEng: Me sorry. Me no can see you later.
Text: 나 미안해. 나 나중에 못 봐.

TextEng: Look, buddy - I came here to learn, not to get hit on by pathetic, lonely losers!
Text: 이봐, 친구 - 난 여기 배우러 왔지, 한심하고 외로운 찌질이한테 작업 당하러 온 게 아니야!

TextEng: Flattery - I like it.
No offense, but I'm not interested.
Text: 기분 나쁘게 받아들이진 말고, 관심 없어.

TextEng: Me like what you say.
Me here for training! Me not care 'bout this stuff!
Text: 나 여기 훈련하러 왔어! 나 이런 거 관심 없어!

TextEng: You be sad little man. Me no want be friend with you!
Text: 너 슬픈 작은 사람이야. 나 너랑 친구 하기 싫어!

TextEng: Actually I'm not seeing anyone right now.
Text: 사실 지금 아무도 만나고 있지 않아.

TextEng: That's really none of your business, Gilbert.
Text: 그건 네가 상관할 일이 아니야, 길버트.

TextEng: Me not seeing anyone right now.
That not be none of you business, Gilbert!
I'd like that, Gilbert.
Sorry, but I'm not interested.
Uh... I'm already going with somebody. Sorry, Gilbert.
Text: 어... 나 이미 누군가랑 가기로 했어. 미안해, 길버트.

TextEng: Me like that, Gilbert.
Me not interested. Sorry.
Uh... me got date already. Sorry, Gilbert.
Text: 어... 나 이미 약속 있어. 미안해, 길버트.
